    "hide_custom_blocks": "true",
    "long_instructions": "##Wolf in Sheep’s Clothing\r\n**What is the wolf's motivation?**\r\n- The moral of this story is **liars are eventually discovered and pay for their actions**\r\n- Read each quote in the dropdown menu of the `think` block\r\n- Choose the quote that most closely matches the character’s personality\r\n- Connect it under the `when run` chunk of code\r\n- Click \"Run\"",
